{"tid":577147,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日食雞食到陣騷味","createTime":"2018-03-01T13:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T16:22:15.000Z","uid":155487,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ecce97c43764386e5fc3ae131b0674b9eebf36be","tid":577147,"uid":155487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"好奇怪既騷味 有時仲好濃<br />\n話佢冰鮮所以有雪藏味又唔見其他肉類會咁<br />\n係雞柳 雞扒既身上發生率特別高<br />\n有時同一間餐廳 一時食冇事 一時又勁臭<br />\n本身好鍾意食雞 宜家都唔敢嗌<br />\n最奇怪係 每次同fd一齊食<br />\n問佢地覺唔覺得臭<br />\n佢地係唔覺既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算覺 都只係話 有少少唔新鮮 然後照食<br />\n但我真係覺得好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟係咪變咗質架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659327ab7302b3fc8bfa81c7b6e1bf147aa2d6a7","tid":577147,"uid":156331,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"093dd3eb0d698c0b90f9dab77acee6f74b5bef29","tid":577147,"uid":8867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10daf3bcf4ef6db569d24241aebf9206b57bc74a","tid":577147,"uid":174074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"我都會！但淨係食雞翼先咁 <br />\n一食超市啲雪藏雞翼就好想嘔"},{"pid":"08b9304467912647264648775490fa1c774f6b29","tid":577147,"uid":16546,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"的確係雪藏味，不過真係有好多人分唔出<br />\n試過食個焗雞扒飯，塊雞扒一咬落去勁大陣雪味，即刻冇曬胃口，但個fd話好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650d2061091f8c89412481dd654bc4ef6eb543fe","tid":577147,"uid":3594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"我叫個d 做雌激素味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"