8093599eba91759c25cfa1d9faab4293da787d","tid":577147,"uid":155487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10daf3bcf4ef6db569d24241aebf9206b57bc74a","tid":577147,"uid":174074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"我都會！但淨係食雞翼先咁 <br />\n一食超市啲雪藏雞翼就好想嘔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"我都會想作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"真心次次嘔番出黎 但又覺得自己好冇衣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1869859adf98ea15b70fd71762eb92ef8fe369e0","tid":577147,"uid":62993,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"雪藏野係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要避味好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 街外好多都草草了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講真香港人有正常味覺嘅人唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大部分進食只為生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大部跟本唔知咩叫美味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企老豆老母又唔識煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下面我會講下我處理雪藏雞方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先講下清洗雪藏雞翼，解凍後清洗三次 清洗時要用手鍊血水出嚟，血水會由有軟骨位滲出，清過之後隔水大概至少45分鐘，想快啲就用廚房紙抹乾，再隔水，會見到不斷有血水出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲腥臭味就係從呢啲血水而來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雞柳、雞排清洗相對易，因為無骨，但同樣清洗後要抺乾同隔水，部分腥羶味來自肥油，肥油太厚哥啲就剪走佢。<br />\n<br />\n醃肉方面 <br />\n<br />\n中式通常用白胡椒粉、酒（米酒 紹興都得 只低濃度油就可以），雞粉，鹽、抓醃，另外可加蛋白，增加滑嫩感，注意要抓醃至雞肉吸晒啲醃料，再加生粉保護，最後再加油（多啲啲都唔怕）走油/半煎油時，啲油會出返黎，唔會吸左（除非你油溫太低），落油係防止落鑊時啲肉痴住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n西式方面通常用牛奶、加蒜粉、洋蔥粉、鹽 ，醃肉前可先試左醃料味道先 ，調好後醃過夜（雞翼、雞髀），牛奶避味效果好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好適合醃完再上粉漿做炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔想咁煩就買新鮮雞吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a50e2a7a6eb10068647b6900e1289a674cf11bc","tid":577147,"uid":155487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52f6347edeea4d87a8293cfe98d9a55edc7978a6","tid":577147,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"638093599eba91759c25cfa1d9faab4293da787d","tid":577147,"uid":155487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10daf3bcf4ef6db569d24241aebf9206b57bc74a","tid":577147,"uid":174074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"我都會！但淨係食雞翼先咁 <br />\n一食超市啲雪藏雞翼就好想嘔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"我都會想作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"真心次次嘔番出黎 但又覺得自己好冇衣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"臭雞真係垃圾 堅決唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f638161536d4f31da600ddb4c3ca85a8e75bf7","tid":577147,"uid":155487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1869859adf98ea15b70fd71762eb92ef8fe369e0","tid":577147,"uid":62993,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"雪藏野係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s